data.name: Crispy Lemon Herb Chicken Thighs
data.quickTastyDescription: Juicy chicken thighs with a crispy skin, infused with lemon and herbs for a refreshing flavor.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a mixing bowl, combine olive oil, lemon juice, garlic powder, thyme, oregano, salt, and pepper.
Add the chicken thighs to the bowl and coat them well with the marinade.
Place the chicken thighs skin side up on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.
Bake for 25-30 minutes, or until the chicken is golden brown and crispy, and the internal temperature reaches 165째F (74째C).
Let the chicken rest for 5 minutes before serving.
data.modifiersForBase: Crispy skin, lemon and herbs marinade
